The App Commissions (CMS) is used to manage and calculate sales commissions for salespeople. The basic flow includes:

* Define setups for each salesperson. At this stage you can define the basic contractual conditions for each agent (prepayment, settlement period, etc.).

* Define salesperson roles and sales networks

* Set the commission calculation method

* Generate commission entries either manually or through sales documents

* Ability to manage prepayments or commission cost allocation

* Commissions settlement directly through the purchase invoices, or from settlement prospects

